channel.title: No MY updater
channel.description:
This updater has served me well, I grew impatient with it because it wasnt behaving as I wanted
Since I will never look at it again, I believed that I should post it because it is, to be frank, better than everything I have seen publicly
A little note for those who dont know how to use annotations, since I havent released any hooks with multiple dependencies, you would do it something like this: [code]@Dependencies({DeliciousCakeT.class, LaserT.class})[/code] the transformer classes are then automagically sorted on load
deobfuscation classes are not included
If for some reason you actually use this, gimme some <3
<3 Saevion for his directed graph
